      "text": " Oh, I understand now! Here are those font styles written in a casual way:\n\n1. Comic Sans MS - that rounded, friendly font everyone has opinions about\n2. Schulz's Fonts/Peanuts Font - specially made to match Charles Schulz's actual handwriting\n3. Chalkboard or School Book - those slightly messy, handwritten-looking fonts that feel natural and informal",
